title: The Top Crypto Picks If You Missed the Last Crypto Boom: Solana, Near, ScapesMania
description: Explore the evolving cryptocurrency landscape with our analysis of Solana and NEAR Protocol, two of the top crypto picks post the last boom. This article delves into the impact of Bitcoin's ETF rumors on the market, highlighting the significant surge in Bitcoin's market cap and its ripple effect across the crypto world. Gain insights into Solana's remarkable growth in the DeFi sector, its challenges in network stability and scalability, and NEAR Protocol's increasing daily active users and its potential for untapped price growth. This comprehensive overview offers a balanced view of the opportunities and risks in the volatile crypto market, emphasizing the need for a strategic investment approach
